# Role&Roll â€“ FoundryVTT Test System

This is an **unofficial, fan-made** Foundry Virtual Tabletop system created
to experiment with running the **Role&Roll** TRPG on FoundryVTT.

- **Original game:** Role&Roll TRPG  
- **Owner:** BGN Squad  
- **Author of this Foundry system:** Panisara Thepthong  
- **Status:** Personal / testing project, not affiliated with BGN Squad.

## Legal

Role&Roll, and all related game rules, setting, names, and artwork are
the intellectual property of **BGN Squad**. I do **not** own the Role&Roll
system and make no claim to it.

This repository only contains:

- system configuration and code specific to FoundryVTT
- my own implementation of dice mechanics and UI for testing

It is provided purely for personal / experimental use.  
If BGN Squad requests changes or removal, I will comply.

